{"tid":244192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求情緒病巴絲入","createTime":"2017-05-15T08:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T15:24:10.000Z","uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb0344eacfbc92ab1a5410d46cdb00244778f44","tid":244192,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"想問下，如果：<br />\n<br />\n成日好易亂諗野<br />\n經常發惡夢 有時醒返會分唔到係真定現實<br />\n成日都有聲同自己講野咁 有男有女 <br />\n開始控制唔到情緒 會抓自己 或者用指甲「咪」自己，咪到出晒痕先覺得舒服啲<br />\n好易發脾氣 不斷同自己講要冷靜都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n上述情況已經持續左兩三年架喇，最近大半年越來越嚴重<br />\n<br />\n今日訓教又發惡夢，起身完全分唔到現實定真，之後抖唔到氣，跑去廁所嘔，嘔完先好啲。之後手震，又好難抖氣咁。<br />\n<br />\n想問有無巴絲有同樣情況？咁算係咩病？有咩方法可以幫到手？唔想食藥....<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒。"},{"pid":"96b29c2b684445387c6ecd844afa38de89590059","tid":244192,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387f2e293e75b3a150d507fa1ad7be55c140435d","tid":244192,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8ce0f04cbcb295c87fbc7a169844d5428f36cc","tid":244192,"uid":8228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"搵醫生啦..."},{"pid":"5a67aa6762faa9c72658b8fc76256a3465bb40e5","tid":244192,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為自己開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日第一次發惡夢會嘔 好恐怖"},{"pid":"02a3c31812b0978fe7275aadb7491d4a1a9ece19","tid":244192,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵醫生啦...</blockquote><br />\n巴打有睇心理醫生（？）既經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65a584178b65dd